{"type": "article", "id": 22955, "title": "这家科威特咖啡馆的设计，“藏”着一个传统咖啡壶", "description": "事务所的设计围绕着三个元素，展示出来的规划、悬浮的顶蓬和具有功能意义的侧壁。", "date": "2016-02-29T08:03:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15465, "name": "科威特"}, {"id": 16281, "name": "阿拉伯"}, {"id": 2652, "name": "咖啡馆"}, {"id": 24068, "name": "associated architects partnership"}, {"id": 24069, "name": "dallah"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153139hSWnYVNmpe9ofatQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>早在咖啡这种饮料在欧洲盛行之前，它其实是阿拉伯世界里的社交饮品。Coffee 就源于阿拉伯语 Qahwa，在 17 世纪，咖啡的种植和生产被阿拉伯人垄断。直到今天，去阿拉伯国家喝咖啡依然能感受到浓郁的当地特色，咖啡本身散发着香料的味道，喝咖啡也要遵循特定的程序，从特定的器皿里倒出，用手磨碎以表达欢迎之情。</p>\n<p>Dallah 是一种使用上百年的传统咖啡壶，它用金、银、黄铜、铁等金属制作，有着圆鼓的瓶身、优雅的弧形手柄、尖耸夸张的盖子和长喙一样的壶嘴。瓶子表面不忘刻上华丽复杂的花纹，与阿拉伯地区其他器皿很类似。这种咖啡壶影响广泛，在阿联酋迪拉姆硬币的背面就是它的图案。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153133GWAmdQpJOV0xwqI8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153133uQdHCKNlLhAI7rG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>科威特新开了一家名叫 Dallah 咖啡馆，他们使用传统的方式制作咖啡。当地建筑事务所<a href=\"http://www.aap.company/\">associated architects partnership</a> (AAP)被要求设计一个亲和开放的环境，让人们可以在这里分享一杯咖啡。</p>\n<p>事务所的设计围绕着三个元素，展示出来的规划、悬浮的顶蓬和具有功能意义的侧壁。这恰好对应了 Dallah 作为咖啡壶的设计，有图案的瓶身，一个可揭开的盖子和侧面的把手。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153134mKPATZpvDLWlI0t2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153134V9y7xvFmGDcigCXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">透过玻璃橱窗可以清楚地看到里面的布局</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153135iNqcm95IaL1Oun32.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153135kqThitWI4bdjr3y1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">不对称的白色拱形门连接了室内室外</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153136aL1vljreVBcWxEwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65158924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153136dCUAWrMKqtgYPHiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">侧面墙壁做成了木架，有功能性</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">另一侧墙面用六边形和菱形组成具有几何感的图案，非常现代。绿色和白色是阿拉伯国家最常用的颜色，但在一些棕色的菱形图案上，用立体的木板做出翩飞的折纸感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153137MwbBEpX0V9GHfkvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061531377qzrQKAgcwLF0Poj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153138dKXytCJASY4olBGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153138iCuAxyBPJtRjNLQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/aaap-associated-architects-partnership-dallah-coffee-house-kuwait-city-02-25-2016/\"> designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5e4599a60102vqdd.html\">sina</a>、<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Dallah.jpg\">wikipedia</a></p>\n\n\n"}